Format raw IWR data

Source: R/anlz_iwrraw.R
anlz_iwrraw.Rd

Format raw IWR data

Usage

anlz_iwrraw(iwrraw, tidalcreeks, yr = 2022)

Arguments

iwrraw

FDEP impaired waters rule data base as data.frame

tidalcreeks

sf object for population of tidal creeks

yr

numeric for reference year to evaluate, scores are based on the planning period beginning ten years prior to this date

Value

A data.frame with the formatted data

Details

The function subsets the raw IWR data for the selected value in yr and the ten years prior to yr and subsets by the creek population in tidalcreeks. Select water quality parameters in masterCode are filtered and some of the names are combined for continuity.

Examples

anlz_iwrraw(iwrraw, tidalcreeks, yr = 2022)
